node.text: The Boeing 787 Dreamliner is the first airliner that features electro-chromatic dimmable passenger windows that do not require window shades to block out external light. The dimming effect is the result of an electrified gel sandwiched between two thin pieces of glass. As the electric current increases, the gel darkens and as it drops, the gel lightens‼️✈️
